_sText:
If you will use it on a server or know one that will, please tell me :P

This is my first map ever so you know... dont expect too much from it.

I've made so in one map you start with weapons...(Starting Weapons)
And in the other you wont start with guns... (No Starting Weapons)

So that it can be used in DM and such...

This map is made mainly to only use Awp but you can probably use it to more :P

Feel free to remake it if you want...

There are a hidden room under the map... you can get to it by breaking the floor in the corner in the little house...
